headline.print_headline: Holland Helps Maple Leafs Rally Past Senators, 5-3
headline.main: Holland Helps Maple Leafs Rally Past Senators, 5-3

lead_paragraph: Peter Holland had a goal and an assist as the Toronto Maple Leafs erased a one-goal deficit three times in a 5-3 victory over the Ottawa Senators on Sunday night.
